There is POWER in the name of JESUS! 
  Before my house shakes awake and the gift opening begins I must give thanks and remember. 
  My father passed on Christmas morning, December 25, 2020. The Lord welcomed home a warrior angel LTC Bobby R. Harris, while Dad was sleeping. I know Dad prays for me from heaven. Grateful to God for the lives of Jesus Christ, my Dad and all those I love on this holiday. 
  #christmas🙏🏼😇⭐️
Merry Christmas from my family to yours. There is POWER in the name of JESUS! #joytotheworld
